Package sep.gaia.controller.settings

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CacheSettingsListener
    This is to implement the ActionListener Interface to check if the user wants to clear the cache.
    POISettingsListener
    This is to implement the ActionListener Interface to check if the user wants to open the POIEditorWindow.
    SliderListener
    This class is to implement the ActionListener interface to check if the user wants to change the maximal cache size.
    TileSettingsListener
    This is to implement the ActionListener Interface to check if the user wants to add or remove the selected tile server to the tile bar or if the user wants to select a tile server from the list.
